snippet: Jeffery Taylor scored 25 points to lead Sweden to an 81-62 upset of Russia at the European basketball championships in Koper, Slovenia.
abstract: Sweden upsets Russia, 81-62, at European basketball championships in Koper, Slovenia.

headline.main: Russia Upset by Sweden at European Championships
